Class IntMathVec

java.lang.Object
  dr.evomodel.indel.IntMathVec
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable
 class IntMathVec
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable

IntMathVec -- mathematical vector of integers. Vectors provide equals() and hashCode() based on value-identity, so can be used in maps, but are NOT immutable, so take care not to change the value of map-keys.

Author:
Gerton Lunter 20/3/2003
